27B4AD0D.Line7.2CDEB: You may call me Shob'ha. I offer solutions, of a kind, to those in need. Yet it is now I who need aid...

59D74087.Line1.2CDEB: And here you are. Coincidence and opportunity are sisters, you know.

8DC0338B.Line5.2CDEB: If you can find her, I would be in your debt.

F3CBBA09.Line3.2CDEB: An ominous power stirs within the Dark Thicket. I sent my familiar, Berret, to sniff about, but she has been gone too long.
